In [13]:
# 잠깐 분류/회귀로 예측
X = df.loc[:, ['year', 'month', 'day']]
y = df.loc[:, 'label']
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.33, random_state=42)
min_max = MinMaxScaler()
X_train = min_max.fit_transform(X_train)

year, month, day에 대해서 X, y를 통해서 분류방법을 이용하여 여러 가지 모델을 수행을 하였습니다.

Logistic Regression(Classification)¶

In [14]:
lgc = LogisticRegression(random_state=42)
lgc.fit(X_train, y_train)
pred_y = lgc.predict(X_test)
cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(y_test.values, pred_y)

# annotation 준비
group_names = ["TN", "FP (type 1 error)", "FN (type 2 error)", "TP"]
group_counts = [value for value in cf_matrix.flatten()]
group_percentages = [f"{value:.1%}" for value in cf_matrix.flatten()/np.sum(cf_matrix)]
labels = [f"{v1}\n{v2}\n({v3})" for v1, v2, v3 in zip(group_names,group_counts,group_percentages)]
labels = np.asarray(labels).reshape(2,2)

# Metrics 출력
print("Metrics 출력")
print("Accuracy Score", accuracy_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Precision Score", precision_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Recall Score", recall_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("F1 Score", f1_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("ROC AUC Score", roc_auc_score(y_test, pred_y))
TN, FP, FN, TP = cf_matrix.ravel()
TPR = TP / (TP+FN)
FPR = FP / (FP+TN)
print("TPR", TPR)
print("FPR", FPR)
print("------------------------------------------------------------------")

# Confusion Matrix 시각화
sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=labels, fmt='', cmap='Blues')
plt.xlabel('Predicted Label')
plt.ylabel('True Label')

Ensemble - Hard Voting¶

In [20]:
clf1 = LogisticRegression(random_state=42)
clf2 = RandomForestClassifier(random_state=42)
clf3 = GaussianNB()
clf4 = SVC(kernel='linear', probability=True, random_state=42)  # soft voting을 위해선 probability=True 필요
clf5 = KNeighborsClassifier()

voting_clf = VotingClassifier(
    estimators=[
        ('log_reg', clf1),
        ('ran_fst', clf2),
        ('gau_nb', clf3),
        ('svc', clf4),
        ('knn', clf5)
    ],
    voting='hard'
)

pred_y = bagclf.predict(X_test)
cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(y_test.values, pred_y)

# annotation 준비
group_names = ["TN", "FP (type 1 error)", "FN (type 2 error)", "TP"]
group_counts = [value for value in cf_matrix.flatten()]
group_percentages = [f"{value:.1%}" for value in cf_matrix.flatten()/np.sum(cf_matrix)]
labels = [f"{v1}\n{v2}\n({v3})" for v1, v2, v3 in zip(group_names,group_counts,group_percentages)]
labels = np.asarray(labels).reshape(2,2)

# Metrics 출력
print("Metrics 출력")
print("Accuracy Score", accuracy_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Precision Score", precision_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Recall Score", recall_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("F1 Score", f1_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("ROC AUC Score", roc_auc_score(y_test, pred_y))

FPR = FP / (FP+TN)
print("TPR", TPR)
print("FPR", FPR)

def clean_attribute_title(title):
    if pd.isna(title):
        return ""
    # 1. 반점, 느낌표, 물음표 제거
    title = re.sub(r'[,!?]', '', title)
    # 2. 한글과 공백만 남기고 모두 제거
    cleaned = re.sub(r'[^가-힣\s]', '', title)
    # 3. 불필요한 공백 정리
    cleaned = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', cleaned).strip()
    return cleaned
df['title_fix'] = df['title'].apply(clean_attribute_title)

가설 3 - OTT 매체들에 언급되는 콘텐츠에 긍정적인지 부정적인지 키워드에 따라 긍정적인지 부정적인지가 달라진다.(Text Analysis, 분류(Classification) 기법)¶

noun, adjective가 띄어쓰기로 되어 있는 명사, 형용사로 이루어진 리스트¶

In [119]:
def get_only_noun_adjective_list(sentence):
    okt = Okt()
    noun_adjective = []
    for word, pos in okt.pos(sentence, norm=True, stem=True):
        if pos in ('Noun', 'Adjective',):
            noun_adjective.append(word)
    return noun_adjective

우리는 konlpy중 Okt를 이용하여서 Noun - 명사, Adjective - 형용사를 품사 태깅을 이용하여 추출을 한다.

def get_only_noun_adjective(sentence):
    noun_adjective = []
    okt = Okt()
    for word, pos in okt.pos(sentence, norm=True, stem=True):
        if pos in ('Noun', 'Adjective'):
            noun_adjective.append(word)
    return ' '.join(noun_adjective)

df['count_vector_noun_adjective'] = df['comment_fix'].apply(lambda x: get_only_noun_adjective(x))

Logistic Regression(Classification)¶

In [131]:
lgc = LogisticRegression(random_state=42)
lgc.fit(X_train_vectorizer, y_train)
pred_y = lgc.predict(X_test_vectorizer)

cf_matrix = confusion_matrix(y_test.values, pred_y)
# annotation 준비
group_names = ["TN", "FP (type 1 error)", "FN (type 2 error)", "TP"]
group_counts = [value for value in cf_matrix.flatten()]
group_percentages = [f"{value:.1%}" for value in cf_matrix.flatten()/np.sum(cf_matrix)]
labels = [f"{v1}\n{v2}\n({v3})" for v1, v2, v3 in zip(group_names,group_counts,group_percentages)]
labels = np.asarray(labels).reshape(2,2)

# Metrics 출력
print("Metrics 출력")
print("Accuracy Score", accuracy_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Precision Score", precision_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("Recall Score", recall_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("F1 Score", f1_score(y_test, pred_y))
print("ROC AUC Score", roc_auc_score(y_test, pred_y))
TN, FP, FN, TP = cf_matrix.ravel()
TPR = TP / (TP+FN)
FPR = FP / (FP+TN)
print("TPR", TPR)
print("FPR", FPR)
print("------------------------------------------------------------------")

# Confusion Matrix 시각화
sns.heatmap(cf_matrix, annot=labels, fmt='', cmap='Blues')
plt.xlabel('Predicted Label')
plt.ylabel('True Label')
